      "comment": "DADDY COOL (3) had some strong recent form but was below best last time when seventh (25.04) in a Free For All at Sale. Generally a safe beginner but never in it last time. Key runner on his best form. BLACKPOOL FINN (1) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at this track over 390m behind Springer's Boy (22.64) in a Grade 4/5. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. WEBLEC SNOOP (5) is a promising dog in the frame at nine of 14 starts including four wins and was in the minors again latest (16.89) over 300m at Healesville. Goes well from this draw. Will go close here with a clear run. DEADLY FORCE (4) is in fine form and looks a good top-three chance again.",
